imdb.plot outline: Fallen Watcher Angels have children on Earth. These children have abilities. Marcus Kaine, the Avenging Angel, is the son of the Fallen Watcher Angel Sariel. He's Not your average superhero. Death is an option with him. If you try to kill him or if you deserve to die - then your ass is dead. A rule he lives by while protecting the metropolitan area of Chesilhurst City.
